Information:
"Mata Kimi ni Koishiteru / Asia no Kaizoku" is the 37th single released by Sakamoto Fuyumi. It was originally a single A-side called "Asia no Kaizoku", but was later changed to a double A-side in October 2009 with the release of her ninth cover album, Love Songs ~Mata Kimi ni Koishiteru~.
